    public class StandardWTWorkSetService
extends StandardManager
implements wt.change2.workset.WTWorkSetService, java.io.Serializable

    Use the newStandardWTWorkSetService static factory method(s), not the StandardWTWorkSetService constructor, to construct instances of this class. Instances must be constructed using the static factory(s), in order to ensure proper initialization of the instance.
